h2. This is your first task. 
{color:#707070} Issues are the things you do in a project. In business projects, issues are called tasks. {color}
h4. Types of tasks
{color:#707070}A task can represent a document, a creative asset, a purchase and even a person.{color}
!IssueTypes.png!
h4. Details
{color:#707070}The 'Details' section above, provides the information you need, such as priority and status, to help you track the progress of your tasks.{color}
